        "authorId" : "1184220e-bf82-4d6e-80d3-029ead7b5b73",
        "body" : "cb = conda-build3\r\n\r\n> stating that skip selectors were not allowed with noarch.\r\n\r\nThis is true, but you can pin your run-time python to `>=3.3`",
